Description: IvorySQL @IVORY_VERSION@ PostgreSQL @PG_MAJOR@ kernel
 IvorySQL is an Oracle-compatible PostgreSQL fork. This package ships
 IvorySQL @IVORY_VERSION@, based on PostgreSQL @PG_VERSION@, as one complete
 runtime under /usr/ivory-@PG_MAJOR@ with client tools, server binaries, headers, PGXS files,
 procedural languages, and bundled contrib extensions.
